longBusinessSummary: Delta 9 Cannabis Inc. operates as an integrated cannabis company. The company, through its subsidiary, Delta 9 Bio-Tech Inc., engages in the cultivation, processing, extraction, wholesale distribution, retail, and sale of medical and recreational cannabis and related merchandise and devices. As of April 14, 2021, it owned and operated 12 retail stores under the Delta 9 Cannabis Store brand. Delta 9 Cannabis Inc. was founded in 2012 and is headquartered in Winnipeg, Canada.
